channel.title: Ukizai - Fun Server & Pking
channel.description:
[CENTER] [SIZE=5][FONT=Impact]Information: This server is based of Dawntained by MGT Madness. He even asked me to tell him when I was going to start hosting and I've been trying to contact him but hes been offline on Skype. I loved his source setup though and wanted to build off it. This is my first server so I'm hoping to learn from this project. Thanks for taking a look & I hope you can support me on my first try. Thanks Mopar![/FONT][/SIZE] https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xlggWKWmjkI [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/jGhgGpT.png[/img]
[size=36pt][font=impact]Website[/font] [url=http://www.Ukizai.com]www.Ukizai.com[/url] [/size] [FONT=Impact][SIZE=5]Upcoming Updates:[/SIZE][/FONT] New Bosses More Weapon Content More areas and things to do. First Minigame.
